<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - CasinoBot</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-light">
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 mx-auto" style="max-width: 900px">
        <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5">
          <h1 class="fw-bold text-center mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-center text-muted mb-4">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> 29/01/2025
          </p>

          <p class="text-muted">
            CasinoBot is committed to protecting the privacy of its users. This
            Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it,
            and the measures we take to protect it. By using CasinoBot, you
            agree to the terms described in this policy.
          </p>

          <hr class="my-4" />

          <h3 class="fw-semibold">1. Information Collected</h3>
          <p>
            We collect the following data to ensure CasinoBot works properly:
          </p>

          <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-3">User and Server Data</h5>
          <ul class="mb-4">
            <li><code>userId</code>: Unique Discord user ID.</li>
            <li><code>guildId</code>: Unique Discord server ID.</li>
            <li><code>lang</code>: Server language setting.</li>
            <li><code>economyType</code>: Economy system status.</li>
            <li>
              <code>balance</code>, <code>level</code>, <code>experience</code>:
              User’s progress information.
            </li>
            <li>
              <code>swag</code>: Virtual items obtained (balloons, mobiles,
              bikes).
            </li>
            <li>Command and game activity history.</li>
            <li><code>votes</code>: Reward multiplier based on user voting.</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="fw-semibold">Payment Data</h5>
          <p>
            CasinoBot may offer premium features.
            <strong>We never store financial information</strong>; all
            transactions are processed securely by third parties.
          </p>

          <hr class="my-4" />

          <h3 class="fw-semibold">2. Use of Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Enable bot functions and commands.</li>
            <li>Personalize user experience.</li>
            <li>Maintain user progress in the economy and gaming system.</li>
            <li>Provide benefits to VIP users and voters.</li>
            <li>Ensure security and stability of CasinoBot.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-4">3. Data Protection</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Advanced security measures prevent unauthorized access or leaks.
            </li>
            <li>
              Data is used exclusively by CasinoBot and never shared with third
              parties.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong
                >CasinoBot does not store sensitive or financial data.</strong
              >
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-4">4. Sharing Data with Third Parties</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>No sale or distribution</strong> of personal data.</li>
            <li>
              Data may only be disclosed if required by law or for security
              reasons.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-4">5. Data Retention and Deletion</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Data is kept as long as needed for bot functionality.</li>
            <li>Users can request deletion according to Discord’s policies.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h3>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Check it
            occasionally to stay informed about any changes.
          </p>

          <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-4">7. Contact</h3>
          <p>
            If you have questions, join our Discord support server and contact
            the team.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
